bject's removal.  \n  \n### Syntax  \n  \n```  \nHRESULT get_view_removed_reason() const throw();  \n```  \n  \n \n## See Also  \n [Concurrency Namespace (C++ AMP)](concurrency-namespace-cpp-amp.md)\n"}